reviewText: This is by far one of the worst play movies I have seen.  I am so tired of silly plots and endless insults within the script amongst our culture.  The underlying Christian message was a stretch.The other thing that bothers me is that I am so tired of the portrayal of the infidelities that exist.  Can you actually have a play with legitimate issues that don't involve cheating.  It makes me sick to my stomach but funny how once caught everyone is sorry.Don't waste your time on this.
summary: One of the worst I have seen.....don't waste your money or time
